{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"9":{"eng-name":"Zakat (Kitab Al-Zakat)","ara-name":"كتاب الزكاة"}},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1556,"hadithnumber_last":1700,"arabicnumber_first":1556,"arabicnumber_last":1700}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1681,"arabicnumber":1681,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن كثير، اخبرنا اسراييل، عن ابي اسحاق، عن رجل، عن سعد بن عبادة، انه قال يا رسول الله ان ام سعد ماتت فاى الصدقة افضل قال \" الماء \" . قال فحفر بيرا وقال هذه لام سعد","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":126},"chapter":{"id":42,"ara-name":"باب فِي فَضْلِ سَقْىِ الْمَاءِ","eng-name":"On The Excellence Of Supplying Drinking Water","isFirstHadith":false}}]}